<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.10">
<l>kuṉṟa meṭuttā niraikāt tavaṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>maṉṟil pukaḻmaṅ kaimaṉka likaṉṟicol</l>
<l>oṉṟu niṉṟavoṉ patumval lavartammēl</l>
<l>eṉṟum viṉaiyā yiṉacā rakillāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Existent karma will not ever be able to press upon</l>
<l>Those who master these one-and-remaining nine [verses],</l>
<l>The words of Kalikaṉṟi, king of Maṅkai [which is] famed in assemblies,</l>
<l>About him who protected the cowherd, lifting a mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
